' Modelo final del Observatorio Económico y de Mercados de Bolivia
' Fuente: elaboración propia basada en SDMX 3.1, GSIM 2.0, UN-NQAF e INE Bolivia.
' Archivo autónomo: no requiere includes externos.

@startuml
title Estado — dataset_version
skinparam shadowing false
[*] --> DRAFT
DRAFT --> UNDER_REVIEW : submitForReview
UNDER_REVIEW --> DRAFT : requestChanges
UNDER_REVIEW --> APPROVED : approve
UNDER_REVIEW --> REJECTED : reject
APPROVED --> PUBLISHED : publish
PUBLISHED --> SUPERSEDED : publishSuccessor
PUBLISHED --> WITHDRAWN : withdraw
REJECTED --> DRAFT : reopen
REJECTED --> [*]
SUPERSEDED --> [*]
WITHDRAWN --> [*]

note right of PUBLISHED
Solo una versión puede ser
is_current=true por dataset.
end note
@enduml
